ArticleText:
小魯書讀得少，6743應該算不上防疫概念才對，就了解是從事聲音科技醫療相關，參考如
下。

https://i.imgur.com/W9zBZJO.jpg

A. Smart Headsets
　1. Console Gaming Headsets;
　2. PC Gaming Headsets;
　3. iPhone/iPad/iPod Lightning Headsets;
　4. Android/PC USB/USB C Headsets;
    5. Bluetooth/Proprietary 2.4GHz Wireless Headsets.

B. Smart Speaker Boxes
　1. Conference Speaker Boxes;
　2. Smart Voice Speaker Boxes.

C. Key Components
1. Lightning and USB/USBC cables;
2. Speaker drivers;
3. Acoustic filming;
3. Over molding/double molding/triple material injections;
4. Noise canceling and noise reduction technologies

請各位溫拿指點，或許是大家開始戴耳機上課？
